==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Timely
<hw>Time"ly</hw> <pr>(t⟦imac⟧m"l⟦emac⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos> <adjf>Timelier</adjf>
<pr>(t⟦imac⟧m"l⟦emac⟧*⟦etil⟧r)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
<adjf>Timeliest</adjf>.]</amorph> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Being or occurring in
good time; sufficiently early; seasonable.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>timely</xex> dew of sleep.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Keeping time or measure.</def>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Timely</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Timely
<hw>Time"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Early; soon; in good
season.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Timely</qex> advised, the coming evil shun.</q>
<rj><qau>Prior.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thanks to you,⟦br⟧
That called me <qex>timelier</qex> than my purpose hither,⟦br⟧
For I have gained by it.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Timenoguy</ent>⟦br⟧
